textcanvas 131109 "The Idea is the following:
  * BaseForm represents the calculation scheme of the bilinear forms
  * IntegratorDescriptor is the wrapper, which determines ON WHICH Matrix the element matrix gets assembled to
  * Assemble performs the loop over all IntegratorDescriptors of all regions"
  font small_bold  xyzwh -351 -97 2000 698 163
note 131237 "for i in all integrators_ {
  BaseForm * b = integrators_[i]->GetIntegrator();
  destMat = integrators_[i]->GetDestMat();
  for e in all elements of this region {
    Matrix m = b->CalcElementMatrix(e);
    algsys->SetElementMatrix(m, destMat);
  }
}
  "
  xyzwh 529 386 2000 277 204
